output.analysis:
Let me analyze this post according to the given criteria:
1. CMF presence: Yes, CMF 11240014 is present, indicating this is official electoral content
2. Candidate reference: - Mentions George Simion (presidential candidate) in the title - Also mentions Ovidiu Cupșa, an AUR Senate candidate
3. Wide population targeting: - This is a paid advertisement - Targeting Facebook and Instagram platforms - Large impression range (25,000-30,000) - Estimated audience size over 1 million
4. Electoral objective: - The title "Susține George Simion" is a clear call for support - Features candidates from AUR - Official party communication (has CMF)
5. Journalism vs Propaganda: - This is clearly marked as political content - Not journalistic as it's commissioned by AUR - Contains direct promotion of candidates
6. Personal Opinion: - This is not a personal opinion but an official party communication

conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This post constitutes electoral propaganda because: - It's a paid political advertisement - Has official CMF number - Directly promotes candidates - Large scale distribution - Clear electoral objective in supporting George Simion and AUR candidates - Is running during the presidential campaign blackout period while mentioning a presidential candidate
conclusion.message-for-police: Alianța pentru Unirea Românilor și SC Total Marketing SRL, pentru incalcarea articolului 55 t) din Legea 370/2004, prin difuzarea de materiale de propagandă electorală după încheierea campaniei electorale pentru alegerile prezidențiale, respectiv postarea cu ID-ul 562641266468758 pe platforma Facebook. Materialul promovat conține referințe directe la candidatul prezidențial George Simion, fiind difuzat după ora 18:00 pe 23.11.2024, într-un mod care încalcă perioada de black-out electoral. Postarea are caracter electoral evident, fiind comandată de partid (CMF 11240014), și a ajuns la un public de 25.000-30.000 persoane prin promovare plătită.
